description: Eating a banana triggers something in Nate Summers that makes him feel like showing off for us in Scene Three. In a sizzling-hot solo performance, Summers mounts dildos of all shapes and sizes, proving that his hole is as wide as it is deep! From the balcony to the backyard, Summers shows us what he can do - and he does it well!
title: Wristrider, Scene #03
